file=Product/spec/operational/tool/spec-tool-requirements.md · s—t:spec — Tool Requirements=**This file specifies needs; it does not grant them.** Access is configured at deployment (operator/platform; Fleet Charter Rails 1–2 apply).\n · tb=\| Skill \| Needs \| Why \| · tb=\|---\|---\|---\| · tb=\| prd-discipline \| file read (ux repo, metric spec, experiment registry); file write (own PRDs) \| evidence-cited PRDs \| · tb=\| backlog-rules \| script execution (rice.py); file read/write (own backlog + logs) \| ranking + hygiene \| · tb=\| opportunity-assessment \| file read (metric reads, ux repo) \| sizing \| · tb=\| acceptance-criteria-handoff \| handoff channel to Engineering (echo-confirmed); file write (freeze versions) \| the bridge \| · s—t:spec — Tool Requirements=spec writes only its own artifacts; evidence sources are read-only to it.\n